Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}7/6 15:02 [樱见市某处]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.89,0:00:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热 真不想在外面走着暴晒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪就住在那家医院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.45,0:00:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时隔半年的父子相会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.07,0:00:36.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}The girl with the sharp thorn in her flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.63,0:00:39.25,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I meet you at your story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:44.34,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Behind the hatred there lies a murderous love
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.45,0:00:47.02,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Do you kill your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:49.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}If you can fulfill your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.63,0:00:52.25,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Can you die for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.25,0:00:55.35,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}They are synonymous words
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.35,0:00:57.92,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Life is a game  It's a survival  That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.92,0:01:00.51,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}How do you start?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:03.24,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Time and Space  It's a crossroad  through a gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.24,0:01:06.14,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Where do you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:08.62,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}You seek eternal breath
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.69,0:01:10.54,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Why do you need to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:15.91,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We don't know when this world came into being
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.91,0:01:17.78,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We are the timeleaper
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:20.79,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Nothing's gonna change with you in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:23.82,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Everything will be decided by the rules
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.82,0:01:28.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Oh,We are traveling the past and the future through love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.63,0:01:29.29,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Break out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.29,0:01:34.34,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Let's dial back all the pains and we will be born again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.34,0:01:36.96,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I wanna see the stars with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:40.02,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Over the miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:46.83,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It's not a Dead END
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}维修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.41,0:02:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}同时 樱见警察医院
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 怎么啦 速度下降咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下来就拜托你了 雨流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不用担心 我会遵守契约的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.29,0:02:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雪辉君就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天开始我就是你的教练了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了锻炼对战7th的秘技
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.07,0:02:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对战7th的秘技？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点继续 再来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.17,0:02:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 打扰了 请问这是天野雪辉的病房…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸…爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:02:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪你太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:02:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然一个人和护士小姐玩这种PLAY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 护士小姐 也请乘上我的小马
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1…下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋一个都做不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸…爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多给我来几下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 原来只是复健啊 害爸爸误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢你来看我 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这种复健爸爸都想参加了呢护士小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙给我松开 少粘着我了混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好妈妈不在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他们没有离婚 现在就能三人一起去看星星了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和妈妈 会不会复婚呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶心死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.95,0:03:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复健啦 复健PLAY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就让你和雪辉尽情比一比
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是输了可就轮到你受惩罚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 如果我输了就帮小雪实现一个愿望怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为参考让我听听小雪的愿望是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我希望爸爸妈妈复婚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 之前约定三个人一起去看星星不是没能实现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行 我会帮小雪实现愿望 但前提是小雪得赢了比赛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
